'''2015年共和遊行'''（{{lang-fr|marches républicaines}}），是指在[[法國|法國]]當地時間2015年1月10日至11日間，於各城市所舉辦的[[遊行|遊行]]，其中以[[巴黎|巴黎]][[共和國廣場_(巴黎)|共和廣場]]的規模最大。遊行的目的是為了聲援[[查理周刊总部枪击案|查理周刊总部枪击案]]、[[沙尔利周刊总部枪击案#蒙鲁日枪击案|蒙魯日槍擊案]]和[[查理周刊总部枪击案#文森門脅持案|文森門脅持案]]的受害者，並為支持[[言論自由|言論自由]]發聲<ref name="BB9JAN">{{cite news | url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2015-01-09/shots-fired-hostages-taken-in-town-northeast-of-paris.html | title=Paris Terror Suspects Killed in Twin French Police Raids | work=Bloomberg | date=9 January 2014 | accessdate=11 January 2015 | archive-date=2015-01-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150113034048/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2015-01-09/shots-fired-hostages-taken-in-town-northeast-of-paris.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。法國官員估計，此場遊行有超過370萬人參加，是自1944年[[二戰|二戰]]結束，慶祝[[解放巴黎|巴黎被解放]]的大遊行後，法國規模最大的公眾集會。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Hinnant|first1=Lori|last2=Adamson|first2=Thomas|title=Officials: Paris Unity Rally Largest in French History|url=http://hosted.ap.org/dynamic/stories/E/EU_FRANCE_ATTACKS_RALLY?SITE=AP&SECTION=HOME&TEMPLATE=DEFAULT&CTIME=2015-01-11-12-51-46|accessdate=11 January 2015|work=Associated Press|date=11 January 2015|archive-date=2015-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150111213526/http://hosted.ap.org/dynamic/stories/E/EU_FRANCE_ATTACKS_RALLY?SITE=AP&SECTION=HOME&TEMPLATE=DEFAULT&CTIME=2015-01-11-12-51-46|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=bbcnews>{{cite news|title=Paris attacks: Millions rally for unity in France|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-30765824|accessdate=12 January 2015|work=BBC News|date=12 January 2015|archive-date=2015-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150112015430/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-30765824|dead-url=no}}</ref>

